Bit Manipulation

Bitwise operators:

1. AND - & (1 only when both the bits are set)
2. OR - | (1 when atleast 1 bit is set)
3. XOR - ^ (gives 1 when both bits are different)
4. LEFT SHIFT  <<  
5. RIGHT SHIFT >>
6. NOT ~



Left Shift operator

4 :     00000.....0100 

4 << 1  00000.....1000


Right shift operator
4 :     00000.....0100 

4 >> 1   0000.....0010